WEBVTT

00:06:31.621 --> 00:06:34.434
Wazazi wetu sote
kama watu wanavyowaita,

00:06:34.458 --> 00:06:35.617
Adam na Hawa,

00:06:35.641 --> 00:06:39.799
wasigeweza kufa, alimradi waliendelea kula
kutoka kwenye mti wa uzima.

00:06:40.631 --> 00:06:42.829
Ila punde walivyoanza kula

00:06:42.853 --> 00:06:45.435
kutoka kwenye mti wa maarifa,
ya mema na mabaya,

00:06:45.459 --> 00:06:47.263
wakaanguka kutoka kwenye weupe wao.

00:06:47.808 --> 00:06:50.833
Wakajawa na aibu na uwoga,

00:06:50.857 --> 00:06:52.054
wakajitambua.

00:06:52.865 --> 00:06:55.233
Na wakajifunza,
kwa kuchelewa, pengine,

00:06:55.257 --> 00:06:57.997
kwamba kwa kweli kuna vitu
tunahitaji kuvijua,

00:06:58.021 --> 00:07:01.968
lakini kuna vingi, vingi zaidi
ambavyo ni bora visichunguzwe.